{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01X7vLaifsehNRhwSvtXBWbr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear: \n1. `crdb-cluster-0` is running but not ready because it can't find `crdb-cluster-1` and `crdb-cluster-2` (those pods don't exist yet)\n2. The StatefulSet is in `OrderedReady` mode (default), meaning it only creates the next pod when the previous one is ready\n3. Since pod-0 is not ready (readiness probe returns 503), pods 1 and 2 are never created\n\nThe fix is to use `podManagementPolicy: Parallel` in the StatefulSet so all pods are created simultaneously. \n\nCockroachDB expects all nodes to start up and discover each other through gossip before the cluster is initialized with a single `cockroach init` command. Since `podManagementPolicy` is immutable after creation, I'll need to delete the StatefulSet and recreate it with the parallel policy enabled.\n\nThe PVCs will persist through this operation since they're created from volumeClaimTemplates and won't be automatically deleted when the StatefulSet is removed.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3626,"cache_read_input_tokens":31094,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3626},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"54a9ab3b-2f79-4d3b-8e6a-da1629f24459","uuid":"c3212e6f-eacf-4ef0-b861-3c6f7c01535e","request_id":"req_011CccBEFyGxLR2oVnQmF8Xs"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01X7vLaifsehNRhwSvtXBWbr","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The StatefulSet is deadlocked: pod-0 needs pod-1 and pod-2 to join, but the default `OrderedReady` policy won't create pod-1 until pod-0 is ready. I need to switch to `podManagementPolicy: Parallel`. Since that field is immutable, I'll delete and recreate the StatefulSet (PVCs are preserved)."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3626,"cache_read_input_tokens":31094,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3626},"output_tokens":27,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"54a9ab3b-2f79-4d3b-8e6a-da1629f24459","uuid":"ec4bb5f1-7115-4a00-899c-cf4d32a0a3e2","request_id":"req_011CccBEFyGxLR2oVnQmF8Xs"}
